erase inhibitor.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/65777/', '', 'Ginkgo biloba, Aducanumab', 'Tinidazole, Pantoprazole, Tetracycline, Dexlansoprazole, Rabeprazole, Sucralfate, Misoprostol, Bismuth subcitrate potassium, Rifabutin, Nizatidine, Esomeprazole, More', 1767369485);
